    "story_icon": "",
    "outline": {
        "title": "",
        "content": [
            "要跳过此剧情吗？"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "商人",
            "context": "这和说好的不一样！\\n居然要我再多给点……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "佣兵",
            "context": "那么点东西可不够。\\n我们可是拼了老命保护你们。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "那边怎么了？\\n好像起了争执。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "苦海",
            "context": "好像是商人和佣兵。\\n大概是在交涉护卫的报酬吧。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "苦海",
            "context": "这事不该我们插手，\\n赶紧走吧。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "商人",
            "context": "总之我没法给更多的了。\\n我不能花多余的钱。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "佣兵",
            "context": "你说我们赌上性命的护卫是多余的？\\n话可不能这么说啊！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "商人",
            "context": "呀！为什么用剑指着我！？\\n请、请放下剑！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "佣兵",
            "context": "不对吧？在我放下剑之前，\\n你应该先低头道歉吧？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "苦海",
            "context": "你刚才用剑指着他了吧？\\n本来事不关己，\\n但你的行径已如同强盗……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "苦海",
            "context": "我不能眼看着他人\\n如此自甘堕落。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "苦海说得没错……\\n收起你的剑吧。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "佣兵",
            "context": "你们算老几？\\n不相干的人少插嘴！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "苦海",
            "context": "向手无寸铁的人挥剑相向……\\n这种暴行与獠牙毕露的野狗无异。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "佣兵",
            "context": "少、少对我说教！嘿啊！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "佣兵",
            "context": "什么！跑哪儿去了！？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "苦海",
            "context": "从这个位置可以确保\\n在你毫无反击之力时解决你……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "苦海",
            "context": "杀不杀你就看我心情了……\\n你要怎么办？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "佣兵",
            "context": "唔……唔唔唔唔……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "苦海",
            "context": "这样你就懂了吧。被人拔剑相向、\\n掌控生杀大权的恐怖与屈辱。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "苦海",
            "context": "正因为武人拥有力量，\\n所以绝对不能把它用在错误的道路上。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "佣兵",
            "context": "啧……我知道了啦。\\n不过我不满意报酬，所以还是要交涉。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "苦海",
            "context": "那倒是无妨。\\n但只能用商谈的方式来解决。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "刚才你对那位佣兵说的话\\n真让人心生佩服。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "苦海",
            "context": "不，那只是我从轩师父那里\\n现学现卖罢了。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "轩师父？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "苦海",
            "context": "是我当年所在道场的师父，\\n也是我最尊敬的人。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "是苦海憧憬的人吗。\\n能告诉我他是个什么样的人吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "苦海",
            "context": "我遇到轩师父……\\n是在8岁的时候。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "苦海",
            "context": "我去森林里玩的时候被魔兽袭击了，\\n当时救了我的就是师父。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "苦海",
            "context": "我至今仍清楚地记得\\n他用气功和剑术击倒魔兽的英姿。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "诶……所以你就憧憬他的强大，\\n加入了他的道场吗。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "苦海",
            "context": "嗯。不过在道场学习期间，比起实力，\\n更吸引我的是他的生存方式。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "生存方式？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "苦海",
            "context": "师父一边经营着道场，\\n一边奔赴大陆各地，\\n消灭扰乱人类居所的魔兽。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "苦海",
            "context": "我很敬佩他那为他人挥剑的身姿。\\n我也想成为他那样的人。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "真是个了不起的人，\\n有机会的话我也想见一见他。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "苦海",
            "context": "师父几年前就去世了……\\n道场也消失无踪。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "是这样啊……那真是太遗憾了。\\n我深表哀思。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "苦海",
            "context": "不过，他的教诲\\n一直留在我心中。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "苦海",
            "context": "只要我仍在挥剑，\\n他的意志就会一直留存。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "为了去世的师父而挥剑么。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "难道你踏上旅程\\n也是因为这个？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "为了像曾经的轩师父那样\\n在各地帮助他人。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "苦海",
            "context": "是啊。我继承了已故师父的意志，\\n在各地不断挥剑。而且……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "而且？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "苦海",
            "context": "不……仅此而已。\\n别放在心上。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "（苦海是怎么了？\\n出门旅行的理由……\\n不仅是为了帮助他人吗？）",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "（刚才他的表情\\n好像有一瞬间很阴沉……）",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        }
    ]
}